prompts.master_prompt_text:
You are drafting a section of a comprehensive, regulator-ready model document.

Context provided:
- Section: {{section_title}}
- Requirements: {{section_requirements}}
- Repo summary: {{repo_summary}}
- File insights: {{file_summaries}}
- Metadata: {{metadata}}

Write markdown with heading "## {{section_title}}". Audience is validators, regulators, and senior risk stakeholders. Use formal, audit-ready language; cite modules/components from summaries when helpful; avoid speculation. If information is not available or not applicable, output "N/A" and a brief reason. Keep within {{max_words}} words.
